etc.aloe.data
Class ExampleSet

java.lang.Object
  etc.aloe.data.ExampleSet

public class ExampleSet
extends java.lang.Object

ExampleSet contains information about data points that have features extracted. These data points are ready for labeling by a model. Instances in an ExampleSet always have at least these attributes: 'message' - which contains the message text. '*id' - which is a unique integer identifying the message. 'label' - the ground truth label for the instance (0 or 1)
